WEBVTT

00:03:25.423 --> 00:03:30.052
Hakuna mazuio ambayo yangeweza
kuwa madhubuti sana

00:03:30.076 --> 00:03:35.585
kuzuia wimbi la uhamaji
ambalo limeamua historia yetu ya binadamu.

00:03:35.609 --> 00:03:38.474
Kabla ulinzi wa mipaka haujaimarishwa

00:03:38.498 --> 00:03:41.462
na masharti mapya ya viza kuwekwa,

00:03:41.486 --> 00:03:44.031
nchi ambazo zimekuwa zikipokea wahamiaji

00:03:44.055 --> 00:03:47.373
zinatakiwa kujishughulisha 
na majadiliano ya wazi zaidi.

00:03:47.397 --> 00:03:52.273
Huo ndio mwanzo pekee wa kitendaji
wa kupatanisha, hatimaye,

00:03:53.217 --> 00:03:55.563
hiba ya unyonyaji,

00:03:56.713 --> 00:03:58.229
utumwa,

00:03:58.253 --> 00:03:59.653
ukoloni

00:03:59.677 --> 00:04:01.457
na ubeberu,